REASONING: Maxi-Cash is primarily a pawnbroker and buyer of luxury items like jewellery, designer bags, and watches
The Maxi-Cash website specifically lists only jewellery, designer bags, and watches as items they buy/sell
COE (Certificate of Entitlement) is a government document for vehicle registration in Singapore, not a physical luxury item
LTA (Land Transport Authority) handles COE bidding and transfers through official channels like ATMs and internet banking
No evidence found that Maxi-Cash deals with COE documents or vehicle registration certificates
